          </td>
          <td style="padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; border-right: 1px solid #e3e6ea;">
            <a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; color: #365899; font-weight: bold;">Photos</a>
          </td>
          <td style="padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; border-right: 1px solid #e3e6ea;">
            <a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; color: #365899; font-weight: bold;">More</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
